Invocation Name: tiny log
Developer Terms of Use
des: Being a parent to a newborn is hard! Add to that you may be taking turns with your special other and then keeping track of how much at and at what time your baby eat last is just hard to remember. Use tiny log to record your baby feedings. Tiny log will then when requested provide you with the amount and time of the last feeding.
